high_descs: Turn around and face the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper on the edge of the coffee table, nearest to you.
Turn to your right and go to the first, brown arm chair, on your left.
Place the newspaper on the seat of the brown arm chair.
Turn around and walk to the TV stand.
Pick up the newspaper on the TV stand, in front of the TV.
Turn around and go back to the first, brown arm chair on your left.
Place the newspaper on the seat of the arm chair, behind the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on the living room chair.

high_descs: Move to the long low brown table in front of the brown sofa in the living room.
Pick up the newspaper that is located on the left hand side.
Turn to the right and move to the 2 large brown recliner chairs.
Place the newspaper on the seat of the chair on the right side.
Turn around and move to the table that the TV is sitting on.
Pick up the newspaper that is on the table.
Turn around and move back to the two recliner chairs near the sofa.
Place the newspaper on the seat of the chair that is  on your right by the other newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Collect two newspapers to be placed on the seat of the right hand side chair.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper in front of the plant on the table.
Bring the newspaper and move so that you are between the end of the coffee table and the rightmost brown chair, then turn right and face the chair.
Put the newspaper down on the seat of the rightmost brown chair.
Move so that you are between the other end of the coffee table and the television stand, then turn left to face the television stand.
Pick up the newspaper from in front of the television.
Bring the newspaper with you to the same spot in front of the rightmost brown chair.
Put the second newspaper down behind the first one on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Move the newspapers to the chair.
